SELECT [o0].[Id] AS [OrderId], [o0].[UserName] AS [BuyerName], [p].[Name] AS [ProductName], [o0].[OrderDate], N'Pending' AS [Status]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_1) [o].[Id], [o].[OrderDate], [o].[ProductId], [o].[UserName]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]

    SELECT TOP(@__p_1) [o].[Id], [o].[OrderDate], [o].[ProductId], [o].[UserName]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    WHERE [o].[AdminId] = @__adminId_0
    ORDER BY [o].[OrderDate] DESC
) AS [o0]
INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
ORDER BY [o0].[OrderDate] DESC
